name: project-2
description: Welcome to my second project! This is my first fullstack website and I wanted to make something fun! Soliloquy (Middle English: from late Latin soliloquium, from Latin solus ‘alone’ + loqui ‘speak’), is a blog website where you can creates posts based off of how you're feeling and write comments about them and use GIPHY API. It's like a fun digital jernal just for you!
